export const Config ={
   User:{
      SIGN_IN:"/v1/api/login",
      SIGN_OUT:"/api/?app=logout",
      Auth: "/api/login",
      Ping: "/us/v1/api/secured/ping",
   },
   Users:{
       FindBy:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/findBy?data=",
       FilterBy:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/filterBy",
       AuthHistory:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/{userId}/history/logon",
       ProfileHistory:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/{userId}/history/profile",
       UserOptions:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/{userId}/info/options",
       PersonalInfo:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/{userId}/info/personal",
       AccountsInfo:"/us/v1/api/secured/user/{userId}/info/accounts",

   },
   Transactions:{
       FilterBy:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfers/filterBy",
       Details:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfers/{transferId}/details",
       Logs:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfers/{transferId}/logs",
       Connected:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfers/{transferId}/connected"
   } ,
   Config:{
       Currency:"/us/v1/api/secured/currencyList",
       VerifyStatusList:"/us/v1/api/secured/verifyStatusList",
       CountryList:"/us/v1/api/secured/countryList",
       UList: "/user/getList",
   },
    Providers:{
        Groups:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/provider/groups",
        Providers:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers",
        Actions:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/actions",
        Cashiers:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/cashiers",
        DeleteProviderGroup:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/provider/groups/{groupId}/delete",
        InsertProviderGroup:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/provider/groups/insert",
        UpdateProviderGroup:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/provider/groups/{groupId}/update",
        DeleteProvider:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/delete",
        InsertProvider:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/insert",
        UpdateProvider:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/update",
        DeleteAction:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/actions/{actionId}/delete",
        InsertAction:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/actions/{actionId}/insert",
        UpdateAction:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/actions/{actionId}/update",
        DeleteCashier:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/cashiers/{cashierId}/delete",
        InsertCashier:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/cashiers/insert",
        UpdateCashier:"/ts/v1/api/secured/transfer/providers/{providerId}/cashiers/{cashierId}/update"
    } ,


}
